### Task Management API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Upload Excel File
POST {{baseUrl}}/rest/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary123

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="chat-evaluation-QnA.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./data/chat-evaluation-QnA.xlsx
--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

API test upload
--boundary123--

###

### List All Tasks (First Page)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/api/v1/tasks?per_page=20&task_type=chat-evaluation
Accept: application/json

###

### List Tasks with Smaller Page Size
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/api/v1/tasks?per_page=2&task_type=chat-evaluation&cursor_max_task_id=9223372036854775807
Accept: application/json

###

### List Next Page Using Cursor (replace "123" with actual next_cursor from previous response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/api/v1/tasks?per_page=2&task_type=chat-evaluation&cursor_max_task_id=92233720368547758078
Accept: application/json

###

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Application Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/info
Accept: application/json

